Pagely,is,a,hosting,and,management,service,for,WordPress,sites,Pagely,hosts,WordPress,sites,and,manages,WordPress,updates,and,other,technical,aspects,of,WordPress,site,management,The,Pagely,Partner,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Pagely,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,accounts,managing,domains,and,managing,account,and,billing,information